            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Use nofollow on paid or sponsored links (better: rel="sponsored"), user-generated content like comments (better: rel="ugc"), untrusted links, and competitor links. Do not apply nofollow to all outbound links.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
